<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Inspire Me</h1>
    <%= DateTime.now.strftime("%B %d, %Y")%>: 
    <h2><%= @inspiration.content %></h2>
    <h4>Forward this inspiration to your friends and let's build something beautiful together. </h4>
    <h4>Take a photo of what this represents to you. Be clever, funny, or inspirational. </h4>
    <div style="background-color: #009B77;, border: none;, color: #fff;, border-radius: 5px;, position: relative;, font-size:24px, width: 300px;, height: 70px;"><%= link_to 'Add photo', "http://inspirely.co/inspirations/#{@inspiration.id}" %></div>
  </body>
</html>
